                        <h2>Disk Storage <span>Disk Storage</span></h2>
                        <h4>Options that support virtual machine disk durability and security</h4>
                        <em><a href="/pricing/1rmb-trial/" id="storage_1rmb-trial">Apply for 1RMB Trial<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></em> <a href="/pricing/pia/" id="storage_pia">Buy Now<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a>
